transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, this is Viagra.

Speaker 2: Hello.

Speaker 1: How are we doing?

Speaker 2: I need to cancel my prescription.

Speaker 1: All right, I'm pulling your prescription.

Speaker 2: Mr. Troy Spence?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I see that you have a prescription from Dr. Den Baron.

Speaker 2: For Viagra 100 mg, 10 tablets, every 30 days.

Speaker 1: You just don't need a refill?

Speaker 2: No, cancel it, please.

Speaker 1: You could pause and order as needed.

Speaker 2: No, cancel, cancel, cancel.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: It's hard enough just to get a hold of you guys.

Speaker 1: Please cancel it.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: All right, so I'll cancel everything, you know.

Speaker 2: Keep in mind the price change if you try to reorder.

Speaker 1: Because they're going to have to get you a new doctor.

Speaker 2: No, thanks. Goodbye. Have a great day.

Speaker 1: Okay.
